<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạlly ʿrft ạlwqt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yạlly ʿrft ạlwqt wʿạrf ạ̹nh qryb yyjy ạlywm
 lạzm tạkẖd bạlk ḥạlạaⁿ lạzm tṣḥy̱ qwạm m ạlnwm
 1- (bạb ạlnʿmẗ mạzạl mftwḥ ậmn bạlly ʿsẖạn mạt
 wạḥtmy fy ạljnb ạlmjrwḥ ạwʿy̱ tkwn zy ạljạhlạt)2
 2- (ạ̉ṣl ạlfạdy jạy qwạm wsạʿthạ ytqfl ạlbạb
 wạlnạym lsh wnʿsạn ybqy̱ mṣyrh hlạk wʿdẖạb)2
 3-(wạlly ʿrfh wạ̉mn byh lạzm yshr ystnạh
 kl ḥyạth tsẖhd lyh ʿsẖạn yfrḥ wqt lqạh)2</lyrics>
